# Build-artifact / VCS excludes for the demo-platform runner image, which uses
# the repo root as its build context (COPY . /workspace). All entries here are
# regenerated or irrelevant inside a container image, so excluding them keeps the
# context small and the runner image lean. App services build from their own
# subdirectories and are unaffected.
.git
**/node_modules
**/.terraform
**/.terraform.lock.hcl
**/.next
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*
**/npm-debug.log*
